{"tid":2049634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專刪中國應用程式　印度Remove China Apps遭Google下架","createTime":"2020-06-03T14:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T20:34:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9d952b419f3e84341d71e1a316b370fb2a6c8823","tid":2049634,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200603/s00005/c5c88e43d8d24177bd532454cce06c2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200603%2Fs00005%2Fc5c88e43d8d24177bd532454cce06c2a.jpg&h=dd5f16db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle周三（3日）宣布將一個聲稱會把手機內所有中國程式「剷走」的受歡迎應用程式（App）下架，指它違反Google部分守則。<br />\n<br />\n這個名為「Remove China Apps」的手機程式由印度推出，自5月底以來已有超過500萬次下載，是Google印度軟件商店中排名最高的免費程式。特別是最近中國和印度在邊境傳出軍事糾紛後，程式的受歡迎程度上升。該程式會掃描用戶手機並剷除中國軟件，例如TikTok和阿里巴巴的UC瀏覽器，之後就會彈出信息：「你很了不起，沒有發現中國軟件了。」<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人周三向路透社證實，該程式因為違反公司規定而被下架。報道引述知情者稱，該程式違反Google有關禁止誤導用戶移除第三方軟件、令第三方軟件失效或改動設備設定的規定。研發有關程式的OneTouch AppLabs在其網頁承認程式被下架，並感謝用戶支持。"},{"pid":"ba33496749f1d93c4deeb7509d87c853218764d1","tid":2049634,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200603/s00005/1591187834254/專刪中國應用程式-印度remove-china-apps遭google下架\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200603%2Fs00005%2F1591187834254%2F%E5%B0%88%E5%88%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6remove-china-apps%E9%81%ADgoogle%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=c3c505ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200603%2Fs00005%2F1591187834254%2F%E5%B0%88%E5%88%AA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6remove-china-apps%E9%81%ADgoogle%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6&h=4847c